name: The ritual beggins
description: This is the first piece of an experimental serie that i call “nature ambience”. In this serie i've tryed to capture the impact of the ambience sounds. So you can put your phones and join us into starting this ritual, you can also close your eyes to have a deeper experience! (It was recorded at 2020, Tocantins, Brasil, in a psychedelic ritual made by me and my friend Caio)
